column5: Had a customer send this to me earlier today.   Take down and delete if not allowed but I thought it was hilarious!
OMG This guy has BALLS  LM  F  AO

Blew my back out afew weeks ago so haven’t been on the ice and had to put my 13 yr old lab down on Friday.    So this put quite the smile on my face this morning.   Turns out the guys were fishing off Johnson beach this morning and I’m literally 2 min away so I made sure to get them a proper shirt!
Hey, I was there too. Not a single mark. Do I get a hoodie ? LMAO  Sorry to hear about the pup bud.  Well done James
That was awesome!!  We just played it in the hut LOL, good for a morning laugh!
